		 <div class="col-sm-6">
			<div class="card">
			  <div class="card-header user-rest-header">REST Services (from the User added Indicators)</div>
			  <div class="card-body">
				<div class="alert alert-info">
					<strong>Info!</strong> These are added by the users and need to be tested by passing a default region, country or PA code. The codes are managed in bulk, but can be overridden. You must be <a href="#" class="use-ajax fancy_login_show_popup">logged in</a> to see the list.
